 "remarks": "Great location! Spacious 2-bedroom, 1.5-bath condo located just steps from Cove Island Park. Conveniently close to I-95, Chelsea Piers, the Train Station, and downtown Stamford. The unit features an open-concept living room with a fireplace and sliding doors to balcony. The living room also includes in-wall satellite speakers with a subwoofer, perfect for entertaining or enjoying movies and music. The primary bedroom offers generous closet space, and the primary bathroom features radiant heated floor for added comfort. The second bedroom is ideal for a guest room, home office, or den.  Additional features include: In-unit washer and dryer. One reserved parking spot in a covered lot and one visitor spot. Additional storage on the ground floor. Fitness center/gym. Elevator in building. Building charges: $150 move-in and $150 move-out.  Good credit is required.",
